                ], 
                "name": "mountain"
            }
        ]
    }, 
    {
        "text": "", 
        "line": 23, 
        "range": [], 
        "entities": []
    }, 
    {
        "text": "The Mask Dance Performance", 
        "line": 24, 
        "range": [
            1915, 
            1940
        ], 
        "entities": []
    }, 
    {
        "text": "", 
        "line": 25, 
        "range": [], 
        "entities": []
    }, 
    {
        "text": "Before leaving the village, I spared my time to watch the famous Hahoe Mask Performance. The performance is a combination of dance and drama, all the performers wear masks.", 
        "line": 26, 
        "range": [
            1942, 
            2113
        ], 
        "entities": [
            {
                "type": "LOC_NOM", 
                "span": [
                    1967, 
                    1974
                ], 
                "name": "village"
            }
        ]
    }, 
    {
        "text": "", 
        "line": 27, 
        "range": [], 
        "entities": []
    }, 
    {
        "text": "This dance has been performed following 800 years of tradition. The performance itself tells the story combining the daily life and conflict between the common people and the nobleman.", 
        "line": 28, 
        "range": [
            2115, 
            2298
        ], 
        "entities": []
    }, 
    {
        "text": "", 
        "line": 29, 
        "range": [], 
        "entities": []
    }, 
    {
        "text": "Some of the performances are used in ceremonies, ritual dances, or theatrical plays. Korean masks are varies, moret than 250 types and shaped similar to human.", 
        "line": 30, 
        "range": [
            2300, 
            2458
        ], 
        "entities": []
    }, 
    {
        "text": "", 
        "line": 31, 
        "range": [], 
        "entities": []
    }, 
    {
        "text": "Not far from the village, there is a mask museum with collection of masks all over the world. Visiting Hahoe Village together also with another historical city in Korea named Gyeongju can\u2019t be missed.", 
        "line": 32, 
        "range": [
            2460, 
            2661
        ], 
        "entities": [
            {
